{"tid":116324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵縱火案】疑犯鄰居買定家居保險：佢經常煲燶煲 間屋差啲著火！ |","createTime":"2017-02-11T10:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T10:20:26.000Z","uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"065f126f5af4e368fe507cf24375e29eb3c04b51","tid":116324,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"昨晚港鐵縱火案，疑犯張錦輝鄰居大爆差點被他燒死，鄰居指張錦輝一家四口搬進柴灣興民邨有三、四年，他指張不照顧家庭，一次煮飯，鄰居憶述說：「佢煲燶幾次煲，差點著火！所以我們要買家居保險！」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n鄰居說疑犯太太一個女人擔起頭家，一人打三份工，而張錦輝不付家用，鄰居說：「佢哋剛搬進來時候，裝修所有費用都係張太俾。」鄰居又指張錦輝爛賭，經常賭馬，有時過大海賭錢，鄰居激動地說：「你不顧家已經衰，還會賭錢，知道他有借貸，每次要老婆幫他還債。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n剛剛新年張太帶仔女回鄉，沒有預老公份，鄰居十分同情張太和一對讀初中的子女，他說：「一對仔女好乖，因為阿媽教得好。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n採訪：陳慧瑩&nbsp;<br />\n攝影：韋平<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_477819_0&amp;i=20170211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_477819_0%26i%3D20170211&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9e8ac93a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_477819_0%26i%3D20170211&h=6d31ea55\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_477819_0&amp;i=20170211</a>"},{"pid":"1190c683cfa1451667a89b9a1e0766344540d985","tid":116324,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66c9f9be3a3019215c94da27d49f528e19e92538","tid":116324,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:16:25.000Z","msg":"聞到陣支那蝗味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f63b575ba0246bc8badea62736f9d4b3e464f9","tid":116324,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T10:20:26.000Z","msg":"廢老係咪全職製造家庭悲劇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}